<li><a href="/wiki/Julian_Symons" title="Julian Symons">Symons, Julian</a>: <i>Bloody Murder. From the Detective Story to the Crime Novel: A History</i> (Harmondsworth, 1974).</li>
<li><i>Waterstone's Guide to Crime Fiction</i>, ed. Nick Rennison and Richard Shephard (Brentford, 1997).</li>
<li>Willett, Ralph: <i>The Naked City. Urban Crime Fiction in the USA</i> (Manchester, 1996).</li>
<li><a href="http://www.classiccrimefiction.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.classiccrimefiction.com/" rel="nofollow">Classic Crime Fiction</a></li>
</ul>
